 的约定，我们定义 广义夸克分布，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
F^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right) & =\frac{1}{2}\int\frac{\dif z^{-}}{2\pi}\left.e^{ixP^{+}z^{-}}\bra{p^{\prime}}\bar{q}\left(-\frac{1}{2}z\right)\gamma^{+}q\left(\frac{1}{2}z\right)\ket{p}\right|_{z^{+}=0,\sbf{z}=0}\nonumber \\
 & =\frac{1}{2P^{+}}\bar{u}\left(p^{\prime}\right)\left[H^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right)\gamma^{+}+E^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right)\frac{i\sigma^{+\alpha}\Delta_{\alpha}}{2m}\right]u\left(p\right)\nonumber \\
\tilde{F}^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right) & =\frac{1}{2}\int\frac{\dif z^{-}}{2\pi}\left.e^{ixP^{+}z^{-}}\bra{p^{\prime}}\bar{q}\left(-\frac{1}{2}z\right)\gamma^{+}\gamma^{5}q\left(\frac{1}{2}z\right)\ket{p}\right|_{z^{+}=0,\sbf{z}=0}\nonumber \\
 & =\frac{1}{2P^{+}}\bar{u}\left(p^{\prime}\right)\left[\tilde{H}^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right)\gamma^{+}\gamma^{5}+\tilde{E}^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right)\frac{\gamma^{5}\Delta_{\alpha}}{2m}\right]u\left(p\right)\label{eq:14}
\end{align}

\end_inset

约定是
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{0123}=1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}=i\gamma^{0}\gamma^{1}\gamma^{2}\gamma^{3}$
\end_inset

。其中
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{q},q$
\end_inset

是夸克场。为了易读性，我们省略了强子态和旋量的极化指标。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于洛伦兹不变性，GPDs 
\begin_inset Formula $H^{q},E^{q},\tilde{H}^{q},\tilde{E}^{q}$
\end_inset

只能依赖于运动学变量
\begin_inset Formula $x,\xi,t$
\end_inset

。为了看出这一点，我们把定义重新写成参考系无关的形式。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
F^{q} & =\frac{1}{2}\int\frac{\dif\lambda}{2\pi}\left.e^{ix\left(Pz\right)}\bra{p^{\prime}}\bar{q}\left(-\frac{1}{2}z\right)\sla{n}_{-}q\left(\frac{1}{2}z\right)\ket{p}\right|_{z=\lambda n_{-}}\label{eq:diel15}\\
F^{q} & =\frac{1}{2}\int\frac{\dif z}{2\pi}e^{ix\left(Pz\right)}\bra{p^{\prime}}\bar{q}\left(-\frac{1}{2}z\right)\gamma^{+}q\left(\frac{1}{2}z\right)\ket{p}\nonumber \\
F^{q} & =\frac{1}{2}\int\frac{\dif\lambda}{2\pi}e^{ix\left(\lambda P^{+}\right)}\bra{p^{\prime}}\bar{q}\left(-\frac{1}{2}\lambda n_{-}\right)\sla{n}_{-}q\left(\frac{1}{2}\lambda n_{-}\right)\ket{p}\nonumber \\
F^{q} & =\frac{1}{2\left(Pn_{-}\right)}\bar{u}\left(p^{\prime}\right)\left[H^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right)\sla{n}_{-}+E^{q}\left(x,\xi,t\right)\frac{i\sigma^{\alpha\beta}n_{-\alpha}\Delta_{\beta}}{2m}\right]u\left(p\right)\nonumber 
\end{align}

\end_inset

对于
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{H}^{q},\tilde{E}^{q}$
\end_inset

，有类似的表达式。其中
\begin_inset Formula $\sla{n}_{-}$
\end_inset

是任意类光矢量，按光锥坐标的约定，
\begin_inset Formula $n_{-}$
\end_inset

投影出
\begin_inset Formula $p^{+}$
\end_inset

分量，
\begin_inset Formula $n_{+}$
\end_inset

投影出
\begin_inset Formula $p^{-}$
\end_inset

分量。如果取质子无穷大动量坐标系，则
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf n_{-}$
\end_inset

与质子运动方向相反。考虑到
\begin_inset Formula $n_{-}$
\end_inset

是类光矢量，物理图像为夸克沿着光锥运动。由于GPDs 在 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

轴boost 下不变，所以表达式的下列形式是等价的：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{q}\left(-\frac{1}{2}\lambda n_{-}\right)\sla{n}_{-}q\left(\frac{1}{2}\lambda n_{-}\right)\Leftrightarrow\bar{q}\left(0\right)\sla{n}_{-}q\left(\lambda n_{-}\right)
\]

\end_inset

即单个夸克沿着光锥运动，与两个夸克沿着光锥的相反方向运动是等价的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
矩阵元的部分应该是洛伦兹不变的，
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

