\end_inset

轴的boost。
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta n_{-}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $Pn_{-}$
\end_inset

并不是boosts 不变的，而
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta n_{-}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $Pn_{-}$
\end_inset

的比例
\begin_inset Formula $\xi=-\left(\Delta n_{-}\right)/\left(2Pn_{-}\right)$
\end_inset

是boost不变的。所以GPDs 只依赖于
\begin_inset Formula $\xi$
\end_inset

。换句话说，它们只能依赖于 plus 动量的比值，而不能依赖于单独的 plus 动量，单独的plus动量在boosts 下只是进行缩放。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi\equiv\frac{p^{+}-p^{\prime+}}{p^{+}+p^{\prime+}}=\frac{-\Delta\cdot n_{-}}{2P\cdot n_{-}}=\frac{-\Delta^{+}}{2P^{+}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
上述的定义的前提是，取胶子的光锥规范
\begin_inset Formula $A^{+}=0$
\end_inset

。在其他规范中，需要一条沿着类光路经的Wilson line 
\begin_inset Formula $W\left[-\frac{1}{2}z^{-},\frac{1}{2}z^{-}\right]$
\end_inset

，连接位于
\begin_inset Formula $-\frac{1}{2}z$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}z$
\end_inset

 的两个场，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W\left[a,b\right]=P\exp\left(ig\int_{b}^{a}\dif x^{-}A^{+}\left(x^{-}n_{-}\right)\right)
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

 表示从
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

的路径排序。本文中的大多数公式和结论都可以轻而易举地推广到这种情况中，对于例外我们会说明。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
运动学变量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
电子在质子上散射，
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

是电子动量，
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

是质子动量：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
k_{1}+p_{1}\Rightarrow k_{2}+p_{2}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=k_{1}-k_{2}=p_{2}-p_{1}$
\end_inset

。考虑到初末态电子满足在壳条件，
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{2}=\left(k_{1}-k_{2}\right)^{2}=2m_{e}^{2}-2k_{1}k_{2}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & m_{e}^{2}-k_{1}k_{2}=m_{e}^{2}-\left(k_{1}^{0}k_{2}^{0}-\vec{k}_{1}\vec{k}_{2}\right)\\
 & =m_{e}^{2}+\vec{k}_{1}\vec{k}_{2}-\sqrt{\left(\vec{k}_{1}\right)^{2}+m_{e}^{2}}\sqrt{\left(\vec{k}_{2}\right)^{2}+m_{e}^{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

可以看成是
\begin_inset Formula $\left(m_{e},\vec{k}_{1}\right)$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\left(m_{e},\vec{k}_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

两个矢量的欧几里得内积减去模积，所以
\begin_inset Formula $m_{e}^{2}-k_{1}k_{2}\le0$
\end_inset

。也就是
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

是一个类空矢量。一般地可以把它写成
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=\left(0,\vec{\Delta}\right)$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
运动学变量的关系为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & m^{2}=p_{2}^{2}=\left(p_{1}+q\right)^{2}=m^{2}+q^{2}+2p_{1}q\Rightarrow-q^{2}=2p_{1}q\\
 & m^{2}=p_{1}^{2}=\left(p_{2}-q\right)^{2}=m^{2}+q^{2}-2p_{2}q\Rightarrow-q^{2}=-2p_{2}q\\
 & q^{2}=\left(p_{2}-p_{1}\right)^{2}=m^{2}+m^{2}-2p_{1}p_{2}=2m^{2}-2p_{1}p_{2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & Q^{2}=2p_{1}q=-2p_{2}q=-2m^{2}+2p_{1}p_{2}\\
 & p_{1}q=Q^{2}/2,\quad p_{2}q=-Q^{2}/2,\quad p_{1}p_{2}=Q^{2}/2+m^{2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left(p_{1}+p_{2}\right)^{2} & =2m^{2}+2p_{1}p_{2}=2m^{2}+2m^{2}+Q^{2}=4m^{2}+Q^{2}\\
\left(\frac{p_{1}+p_{2}}{2}\right)^{2} & =m^{2}+\frac{Q^{2}}{4}=m^{2}+\frac{t}{4}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
非对称光锥参数化
\begin_inset Formula $\left(X,\zeta\right)$
\end_inset

中，初态核子沿着
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

轴。对称参数化
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x,\xi\right)$
\end_inset

中，初末态平均动量沿着
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

轴。两种参数化的转换关系为，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & x=\frac{k^{+}+k^{\prime+}}{p^{+}+p^{\prime+}}=\frac{X-\zeta/2}{1-\zeta/2}\quad\Rightarrow X=\frac{x+\xi}{1+\xi}\\
 & \xi=\frac{2\Delta^{+}}{p^{+}+p^{\prime+}}=\frac{\zeta}{2-\zeta}\quad\Rightarrow\zeta=\frac{2\xi}{1+\xi}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
歪斜度为零
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
沿某个坐标轴的相对论变换为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{c}
E^{\prime}\\
p^{\prime}
\end{array}\right)=\gamma\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & -v\\
-v & 1
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}
E\\
p
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
E^{\prime} & =\gamma\left(E-vp\right)\\
p^{\prime} & =\gamma\left(p-vE\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma=1/\beta=1/\sqrt{1-v^{2}}\ge1$
\end_inset

。不同坐标轴的boost是独立的。首先选择
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=\left(0,\vec{\Delta}\right)$
\end_inset

的坐标系。只作三维转动而不boost不影响
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{0}$
\end_inset

分量，可以通过三维转动选取
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{3}=0$
\end_inset

同时保持
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{0}$
\end_inset

，此时
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
\Delta^{0} & =0\\
\Delta^{3} & =0
\end{cases}\Rightarrow\begin{cases}
\Delta^{0}+\Delta^{3} & =0\\
\Delta^{0}-\Delta^{3} & =0
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

再考虑初末态质子的动量，由
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=p^{\prime}-p=$
\end_inset

可知
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & E^{\prime}=E\\
 & p^{\prime;3}=p^{3}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

由这两个条件，以及初末态质量相等可知，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(p^{\prime;\perp}\right)^{2}=\left(p^{\perp}\right)^{2}
\]

\end_inset

即核子初末态的横向动量绝对值相等。加上
\begin_inset Formula $p^{\prime\perp}-p^{\perp}=\Delta_{\perp}$
\end_inset

，所以有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
p & =\left(E,-\frac{\Delta^{\perp}}{2},p^{3}\right)\\
p^{\prime} & =\left(E,\frac{\Delta^{\perp}}{2},p^{3}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

如果用光锥坐标表示
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \Delta=\left(0,0,\Delta_{\perp}\right),\quad\xi=-\frac{\Delta^{+}}{2P^{+}}=\left(\frac{p-p^{\prime}}{p^{\prime}+p}\right)^{+}=0\\
 & p=\left(P^{+},P^{-},-\frac{\Delta_{\perp}}{2}\right),\quad p^{\prime}=\left(P^{+},P^{-},\frac{\Delta_{\perp}}{2}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

一般把
\begin_inset Formula $\xi=0$
\end_inset

的坐标称为Drell–Yan 参考系。如果核子在
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

方向动量非常大，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
p^{-} & =E-p^{z}=\sqrt{p^{z;2}+p^{\perp;2}+M^{2}}-p^{z}\\
 & \stackrel{p^{z}\to\infty}{=}p^{z}\left(1+\frac{p^{\perp;2}+M^{2}}{2p^{z;2}}\right)-p^{z}=\frac{\sqrt{p^{\perp;2}+M^{2}}}{2p^{z}}\sqrt{p^{\perp;2}+M^{2}}\to0
\end{align*}

\end_inset

可以认为
\begin_inset Formula $p^{-}=0$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
计算中会用到各种动量乘积，由于
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\left(y-\frac{k^{+}}{p^{+}}\right)$
\end_inset

的存在，迫使
\begin_inset Formula $k^{+}=yp^{+}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
k\cdot p=k^{+}p^{-}+k^{-}p^{+}-k_{\perp}p_{\perp}=k^{+}p^{-}+k^{-}p^{+}+k_{\perp}\frac{\Delta_{\perp}}{2}
\]

\end_inset

考虑到
\begin_inset Formula $2p^{+}p^{-}-p_{\perp}^{2}=M_{N}^{2}$
\end_inset

，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
k^{+}p^{-}=yp^{+}p^{-}=\frac{y}{2}\left(M_{N}^{2}+p_{\perp}^{2}\right)=\frac{y}{2}\left(M_{N}^{2}+\frac{Q^{2}}{4}\right)
\]

\end_inset

同理，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
k^{+}p^{\prime-}=yp^{\prime+}p^{\prime-}=\frac{y}{2}\left(M_{N}^{2}+p_{\perp}^{2}\right)=\frac{y}{2}\left(M_{N}^{2}+\frac{Q^{2}}{4}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
2p\cdot p^{\prime}=-\left(p-p^{\prime}\right)^{2}+2m^{2}=Q^{2}+2m^{2}=\Delta_{\perp}^{2}+2m^{2}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
歪斜度不为零
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
不同坐标轴的boost是独立的。首先通过三维转动选取
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta_{\perp}=0$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{3}<0$
\end_inset

的坐标系，即令
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{\mu}=\left(0,0,0,-Q\right)$
\end_inset

，由此可知，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & E^{\prime}-E=0,\quad p^{\prime;\perp}-p^{\perp}=0\\
 & p^{\prime;3}-p^{3}=-Q,\quad Q>0\\
 & \Delta^{+}=-\Delta^{-}=-2\xi P^{+}=\frac{-Q}{\sqrt{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

根据我们的假设，
\begin_inset Formula $p^{3}>p^{\prime;3}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\left(E+p^{3}\right)/\sqrt{2}>\left(E+p^{\prime;3}\right)/\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula $p^{+}>p^{\prime+}>0$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula $\xi>0$
\end_inset

，表达式是一致的。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & P^{+}=\frac{p^{+}-p^{\prime+}}{p^{+}+p^{\prime+}}>0\\
 & P^{+}=\frac{Q}{2\sqrt{2}\xi},
\end{align*}

\end_inset

由
\begin_inset Formula $E=E^{\prime}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sqrt{M_{N}^{2}+\left(p^{\perp}\right)^{2}+\left(p^{3}\right)^{2}}=\sqrt{M_{N}^{2}+\left(p^{\perp}\right)^{2}+\left(p^{3}-Q\right)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

所以有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p^{3}=\frac{Q}{2},\quad p^{\prime;3}=-\frac{Q}{2}
\]

\end_inset

求解
\begin_inset Formula $p,p^{\prime}$
\end_inset

的各个分量，首先有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
p^{\prime+}+p^{+} & =2P^{+}\\
p^{+}-p^{\prime+} & =2\xi P^{+}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

首先可以解出
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
p^{+} & =P^{+}\left(1+\xi\right)\\
p^{\prime+} & =P^{+}\left(1-\xi\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

使用上面的
\begin_inset Formula $P^{+}=\frac{Q}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p^{-}=p^{+}-\sqrt{2}p^{3}=\frac{\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q-\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}}=\frac{\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,\\
 & p^{\prime-}=p^{\prime+}-\sqrt{2}p^{\prime;3}=\frac{\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q+\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}}=\frac{\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,
\end{align*}

\end_inset

综上，
\begin_inset Formula $\xi>0$
\end_inset

时，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p=\left(\frac{\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,\frac{\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,p_{\perp}\right),\\
 & p^{\prime}=\left(\frac{\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,\frac{\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,p_{\perp}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

由
\begin_inset Formula $2p^{+}p^{-}-p_{\perp}^{2}=M_{N}^{2}$
\end_inset

知
\begin_inset Formula $p_{\perp}^{2}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{\perp}^{2}=\frac{1-\xi^{2}}{4\xi^{2}}Q^{2}-M_{N}^{2}
\]

\end_inset

由于
\begin_inset Formula $p_{\perp}^{2}\ge0$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula $\xi^{2}<1$
\end_inset

，再考虑到之前
\begin_inset Formula $\xi>0$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula $0<\xi<1$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
类似地，如果我们假设
\begin_inset Formula $p^{3}<p^{\prime;3}$
\end_inset

,即
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{3}>0$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{3}=Q$
\end_inset

，则此时
\begin_inset Formula $\xi<0$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
P^{+}=-\frac{Q}{2\sqrt{2}\xi},\quad\xi<0.
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sqrt{M_{N}^{2}+\left(p^{\perp}\right)^{2}+\left(p^{3}\right)^{2}}=\sqrt{M_{N}^{2}+\left(p^{\perp}\right)^{2}+\left(p^{3}+Q\right)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

所以有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p^{3}=-\frac{Q}{2},\quad p^{\prime;3}=+\frac{Q}{2}
\]

\end_inset

使用
\begin_inset Formula $P^{+}=-\frac{Q}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p^{-}=p^{+}-\sqrt{2}p^{3}=-\frac{\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q+\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}Q=\frac{-\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,\\
 & p^{\prime-}=p^{\prime+}-\sqrt{2}p^{3}=-\frac{\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}Q=\frac{-\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}Q,
\end{align*}

\end_inset

综上，
\begin_inset Formula $\xi<0$
\end_inset

时，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & P\equiv\left(P^{+},\frac{Q}{2\sqrt{2}\xi},p_{\perp}\right)\\
 & \Delta\equiv\left(-2\xi P^{+},2\xi P^{+},0\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p=\left(\frac{\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}\left(-Q\right),\frac{\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}\left(-Q\right),p_{\perp}\right),\\
 & p^{\prime}=\left(\frac{\left(1-\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}\left(-Q\right),\frac{\left(1+\xi\right)}{2\sqrt{2}\xi}\left(-Q\right),p_{\perp}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

相当于
\begin_inset Formula $Q\to-Q$
\end_inset

，仍然有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{\perp}^{2}=\frac{1-\xi^{2}}{4\xi^{2}}Q^{2}-M_{N}^{2}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Brandon
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在这个坐标系中，初末态核子的平均动量沿着
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

–轴，即
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf P_{\perp}=0$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \Delta^{+}=2\xi P^{+}\\
 & t=\Delta^{2}=\Delta^{+}\Delta^{-}-\sbf\Delta_{\perp}^{2}=2\xi P^{+}\Delta^{-}-\sbf\Delta_{\perp}^{2}\\
 & \Delta^{-}=\frac{t+\sbf\Delta_{\perp}^{2}}{2\xi P^{+}}\\
 & P^{2}=P^{+}P^{-}=M^{2}+\frac{t}{4}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

也就是，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & P\equiv\left(P^{+},\frac{M^{2}}{2P^{+}},0\right)\\
 & \Delta\equiv\left(\xi\left(2P^{+}\right),\frac{t+\sbf\Delta_{\perp}^{2}}{2\xi P^{+}},\sbf\Delta_{\perp}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p\equiv\left(\left(1+\xi\right)P^{+},\frac{M^{2}+\sbf\Delta_{\perp}^{2}/4}{\left(1+\xi\right)P^{+}},\frac{\sbf\Delta_{\perp}}{2}\right)\\
 & k\equiv\left(\left(x+\xi\right)P^{+},k^{-},\sbf k_{\perp}+\frac{\sbf\Delta_{\perp}}{2}\right),\\
 & p^{\prime}\equiv\left(\left(1-\xi\right)P^{+},\frac{M^{2}+\sbf\Delta_{\perp}^{2}/4}{\left(1-\xi\right)P^{+}},-\frac{\sbf\Delta_{\perp}}{2}\right)\\
 & k^{\prime}\equiv\left(\left(x-\xi\right)P^{+},k^{\prime-},\sbf k_{\perp}-\frac{\sbf\Delta_{\perp}}{2}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
非对称参数化
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
除了
\begin_inset Formula $\xi=\left(p^{+}-p^{\prime+}\right)/\left(p^{+}+p^{\prime+}\right)$
\end_inset

的参数化方式，还有一种非对称的参数化。同样选取
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta_{\perp}=0$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{3}<0$
\end_inset

的坐标系，令
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{\mu}=\left(0,0,0,-Q\right)$
\end_inset

，令
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{+}=-\zeta p^{+}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & E^{\prime}-E=0,\quad p^{\prime;\perp}-p^{\perp}=0\\
 & p^{\prime;3}-p^{3}=-Q,\quad Q>0\\
 & \Delta^{+}=-\Delta^{-}=-\zeta p^{+}=\frac{-Q}{\sqrt{2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

由于
\begin_inset Formula $p^{+}>p^{\prime+}>0$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula $\zeta>0$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p^{+}=\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}\zeta}
\]

\end_inset

由
\begin_inset Formula $E=E^{\prime}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sqrt{M_{N}^{2}+\left(p^{\perp}\right)^{2}+\left(p^{3}\right)^{2}}=\sqrt{M_{N}^{2}+\left(p^{\perp}\right)^{2}+\left(p^{3}-Q\right)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

所以有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p^{3}=\frac{Q}{2},\quad p^{\prime;3}=-\frac{Q}{2}
\]

\end_inset

非对称参数化中，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p^{+}=\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}\zeta}\\
 & p^{\prime+}=\left(1-\zeta\right)p^{+}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

从而，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p^{-}=p^{+}-\sqrt{2}p^{3}=\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}\zeta}-\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}}=\frac{\left(1-\zeta\right)}{\sqrt{2}\zeta}Q,\\
 & p^{\prime-}=p^{\prime+}-\sqrt{2}p^{\prime;3}=\frac{\left(1-\zeta\right)}{\sqrt{2}\zeta}Q+\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}}=\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}\zeta},
\end{align*}

\end_inset

综上，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & p=\left(\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}\zeta},\frac{\left(1-\zeta\right)}{\sqrt{2}\zeta}Q,p_{\perp}\right),\\
 & p^{\prime}=\left(\frac{\left(1-\zeta\right)}{\sqrt{2}\zeta}Q,\frac{Q}{\sqrt{2}\zeta},p_{\perp}\right).
\end{align*}

\end_inset

由
\begin_inset Formula $2p^{+}p^{-}-p_{\perp}^{2}=M_{N}^{2}$
\end_inset

知
\begin_inset Formula $p_{\perp}^{2}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{\perp}^{2}=\frac{1-\zeta}{\zeta^{2}}Q^{2}-M_{N}^{2}
\]

\end_inset

由于
\begin_inset Formula $p_{\perp}^{2}\ge0$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula $\zeta^{2}<1$
\end_inset

，再考虑到之前
\begin_inset Formula $\zeta>0$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula $0<\zeta<1$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
两种参数化的关系为，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
X=\frac{x+\xi}{1+\xi},\quad\zeta=\frac{2\xi}{1+\xi}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

